rilling overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse sdrlk on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description seadrill limited incorporated on may   is an offshore drilling contractor providing offshore drilling services to the oil and gas industry the companys primary business is the ownership and operation of drillships semisubmersible rigs and jackup rigs for operations in shallow mid deep and ultra deepwater areas and in benign and harsh environments the companys segments are floaters and jackups the company offers services encompassing drilling completion and maintenance of offshore exploration and production wellsthe company contracts its drilling units primarily on a dayrate basis to drill wells for its customers a dayrate drilling contract generally extends over a period of time covering either the drilling of a single well or group of wells or covering a stated term the company also provides management services to certain unconsolidated companies in which its holds investments the company has a fleet of approximately  offshore drilling units consisting of over  semisubmersible rigs approximately seven drillships and over  jackup rigs in operation and contracts for the construction of approximately  offshore drilling units the companys subsidiaries include north atlantic drilling ltd which focuses on harsh environment offshore drilling operations sevan drilling asa which focuses on owning and operating drilling units and specializes in the ultradeepwater segment and asia offshore drilling ltd which owns and operates approximately three highspecification jackup drilling rigs » full overview of sdrlk company address seadrill ltd parlaville place  parlavihamilton     hm  p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation john fredriksen  anton dibowitz  leif nelson  henrik hansen  des thurlby  » more officers  directors 