 rigs segment operates selferecting tender barges and semisubmersible tender rigs which are used for production drilling and well maintenance in southeast asia and west africa the company was founded on may   and is headquartered in hamilton bermuda see full profile analyst ratings sell under hold over buy number of ratings  full ratings jefferies and credit suisse cut diamond offshore’s target price jul   at  pm et on marketrealistcom bank of america merrill lynch downgraded ensco jul   at  pm et on marketrealistcom seadrill investors and analysts wave goodbye jun   at  pm et on marketrealistcom competitors name chg  market cap diamond offshore drilling inc  b atwood oceanics inc  m nabors industries ltd  b transocean ltd  b rowan cos plc  b competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by dvax  mo  sbux  bidu  amzn  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience contact us – seadrill skip to main content related companies deep sea supply plc frontline ltd golden ocean group limited ship finance international limited seadrill partners llc north atlantic drilling ltd archer clarksons fearnleys as lorentzen  stemoco as rs platou shipbrokers as new york stock exchange oslo stock exchange about us at a glanceour strategyvision and valuesleadership teamour safety culturerelated companies our fleetinvestor relations key financial informationshareholder servicesshare price informationresults centrereports  presentationsnewseventsfactsheetcorporate governancefaqs careersmedia centre image libraryvideoalert service contact us about us at a glanceou