 company was founded on april   and registered on bermuda with an initial equity of usd  million main offices are located in houston on september   scorpion was listed on the oslo stock exchange otc with full listing on december  on november   the first vessel offshore courageous was delivered in  drilling rig operators seadrill and ensco made takeover bids to acquire scorpion offshore on  may  ensco abandoned its bid after seadrill raised its bid to nkr  per share seadrill already owns about  of scorpion offshore historyedit seadrill was incorporated as a bermuda company in may  by the norwegianborn shipping tycoon john fredriksen and listed on the oslo stock exchange in november  in july  it acquired the drilling company odfjell  in september  it purchased a controlling share of smedvig by outbidding noble energy  in  seadrill acquired eastern drilling in may  seadrill outbid ensco plc for scorpion offshore valuing the company at  million in  seadrill conducted an initial public offering of its north atlantic drilling subsidiary which owns harsh environment rigs seadrill continued to own  of north atlantic drilling  in  the company sold the majority of its tender rig and semitender operation to sapurakencana  the company also sold tender rigs t t and the west vencedor to seadrill partners llc  in june  seadrill acquired a majority interest in sevan drilling  in september  a financial company heirs holdings made a “substantial” investment in seadrill’s nigerian unit in november  the company suspended dividend payments as a result of a downturn in the industry  controversiesedit bribery allegationsedit in  petrobras alleged bribery in the negotiations of rig contracts signed by sevan drilling a subsidiary of seadrill in   environmental damage due to rig fireedit main article montara oil spill in november  seadrills west atlas jackup rig which was located on montara field about  kilometers offshore of darwin australia caught fire after the field had been leaking oil for ten weeks the rig was operated by the thai firm pttep for  days gas and oil ran into the timor sea in what was one of the worst environmental disasters in australian history  referencesedit  a b c d e f g seadrill limited sdrl  fourth quarter  results pdf february     seadrill fleet status report  billionaire john fredriksen bets  million more on seadrills recovery motley fool december     update ensco bids for scorpion trumps seadrill offer  may  – via reuters   seadrill forces ensco out of scorpion race upstream online nhst media group  retrieved    seadrill limited consolidated and predecessor financial statements for the periods ending december   and   viking attacks forbes april     seadrill now controls nearly all eastern shares votes rigzone may     seadrill beats ensco in scorpion battle reuters may     north atlantic drilling ltd announces pricing of its initial public offering of its common shares january     norways seadrill says to remain top nadl owner reuters may     sapurakencana buys  bln worth of tender rigs from seadrill offshore energy today february     seadrill limited sells the tender rig t to seadrill partners llc reuters may     seadrill gains majority control of sevan drilling rigzone june     heirs holdings invests in seadrill for nigerian offshore projects oil review africa august     seadrill plunges on dividend suspension as rig market sours bloomberg november     six years after the montara oil spill those who suffered most still seek compensation newscomau august    norway portal energy portal v t e obx companies of norway aker solutions cermaq dnb dno international fred olsen energy frontline gjensidige golar lng marine harvest norsk hydro orkla petroleum geoservices prosafe renewable energy corporation royal caribbean cruises schibsted seadrill statoil storebrand subsea  telenor tgsnopec yara see also companies listed on the oslo stock exchange retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleseadrilloldid categories companies lis