  in june  seadrill acquired a majority interest in sevan drilling  in september  a financial company heirs holdings made a “substantial” investment in seadrill’s nigerian unit in november  the company suspended dividend payments as a result of a downturn in the industry  controversiesedit bribery allegationsedit in  petrobras alleged bribery in the negotiations of rig contracts signed by sevan drilling a subsidiary of seadrill in   environmental damage due to rig fireedit main article montara oil spill in november  seadrills west atlas jackup rig which was located on montara field about  kilometers offshore of darwin australia caught fire after the field had been leaking oil for ten weeks the rig was operated by the thai firm pttep for  days gas and oil ran into the timor sea in what was one of the worst environmental disasters in australian history  referencesedit  a b c d e f g seadrill limited sdrl  fourth quarter  results pdf february     seadrill fleet status report  billionaire john fredriksen bets  million more on seadrills recovery motley fool december     update ensco bids for scorpion trumps seadrill offer  may  – via reuters   seadrill forces ensco out of scorpion race upstream online nhst media group  retrieved    seadrill limited consolidated and predecessor financial statements for the periods ending december   and   viking attacks forbes april     seadrill now controls nearly all eastern shares votes rigzone may     seadrill beats ensco in scorpion battle reuters may     north atlantic drilling ltd announces pricing of its initial public offering of its common shares january     norways seadrill says to remain top nadl owner reuters may     sapurakencana buys  bln worth of tender rigs from seadrill offshore energy today february     seadrill limited sells the tender rig t to seadrill partners llc reuters may     seadrill gains majority control of sevan drilling rigzone june     heirs holdings invests in seadrill for nigerian offshore projects oil rev